-- Portuguese 10-Year Bond Yield Spread Over German Bunds Widens to a Record
-- B y   K e i t h   J e n k i n s
-- 2010-11-08T14:44:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-08/portuguese-10-year-bond-yield-spread-over-german-bunds-widens-to-a-record.html
Portuguese 10-year bonds fell,
driving the yield to a record high relative to similar-maturity
benchmark German bunds.  The extra yield investors demand to hold the Portuguese
debt instead of bunds rose to 442 basis points as of 2:43 p.m.
in London, according to Bloomberg generic data.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Keith Jenkins in London at 
